00129   /* This variable is updated in three ways:
00130       1) by calling CMSIS function SystemCoreClockUpdate()
00131       2) by calling HAL API function HAL_RCC_GetHCLKFreq()
00132       3) each time HAL_RCC_ClockConfig() is called to configure the system clock frequency 
00133          Note: If you use this function to configure the system clock; then there
00134                is no need to call the 2 first functions listed above, since SystemCoreClock
00135                variable is updated automatically.
00136   */
00137 uint32_t SystemCoreClock = 16000000;
